    "headline": "WS Game Company Launches First U.S.-Manufactured Game, Monopoly Americana",
    "summary": "MANCHESTER-BY-THE-SEA, Mass., June 23, 2026--WS Game Company, one of the few premium board game manufacturers with an authorized Hasbro license, today announced the launch of the Monopoly Americana Edition board game, its first game manufactured in the United States. Now available for pre-order at wsgamecompany.com for $80 with expected ship dates in July, the game pays homage to 250 years of American history and culture with an oversized coffee-table-book-styled package design.",
